lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Agnieszka Radwanska and Australian Open champion Angelique Kerber were upset in the opening round of the Madrid Masters on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska, Kerber Have 1st-Round Exits in Madrid
